Problems of lack of testing and attentiveness are among the problems that need to be eradicated between now and 2030.
Early testing and medication are the solution to these diseases.
The disease can kill a person without warning if left untreated.
The disease can be avoided or even cured if the conditions for avoiding it are followed.
